14 Section 4. Section 50-50-103, MCA, is amended to read:
15 "50-50-103. Department authorized to adopt rules -- advisory council. (1) Except as provided in
16 subsection (3), to protect public health, the department may adopt rules relating to:
17 (a) the operation of retail food establishments and cottage food operations. The rules may address
18 sanitation standards related to food, personnel, food equipment and utensils, and facilities and may address
19 other controls, construction and fixtures, and housekeeping.
